OL,6,FThe meeting on August 11, 2014 was
OL,7,Fbetween Belinda Cortes-Martin -
OL,8,FProgramme Director for the Post
OL,9,FOffice's 'Project Sparrow' - along
OL,10,Fwith Andy Parsons - an external lawyer
OL,11,Ffrom Womble Bond Dickinson who was
OL,12,Fhired in to work for the Post Office
OL,13,Fat the time, and independent
OL,14,Finvestigators Ron Warmington and Ian
OL,15,FHenderson.
OL,17,FThis is the latest ITV News exclusive
OL,18,Fin a series unveiling secret tapes
OL,19,Fsurrounding the Post Office and
OL,20,FHorizon IT Scandal:
