OL,6,F'Project Sparrow' was the internal
OL,7,Fcodename the Post Office gave to its
OL,8,Fwork with Second Sight investigators,
OL,9,Fthe Justice for Sub-postmasters
OL,10,FAlliance, and MPs between 2013 and
OL,11,F2015.
OL,13,FIn the fiery exchanges obtained by ITV
OL,14,FNews, Ms Cortes-Martin accuses
OL,15,Findependent investigators of going on
OL,16,F"a fishing expedition" and using
OL,17,F"emotional language" when talking
OL,18,Fabout sub-postmasters being sent to
OL,19,Fprison.
